    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2254030/extras/8c035a1872edcffad8837f2ac9a3a9e1.poster.avif?t=1726051539\" width=600 height=168 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2254030/extras/8c035a1872edcffad8837f2ac9a3a9e1.webm?t=1726051539\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2254030/extras/8c035a1872edcffad8837f2ac9a3a9e1.mp4?t=1726051539\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>体验石器时代部落首领的生活！狩猎、收集资源、交易、吓跑野生动物、寻找宝藏。<br><br>分配资源<br>收集必要的资源以清理瓦砾、抵御老虎的攻击，以及更多内容。以优惠的价格与商人交易资源，并在部落同伴之间分配责任。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2254030/extras/bd54b1c58a9d00d243b98b234145b849.poster.avif?t=1726051539\" width=600 height=168 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2254030/extras/bd54b1c58a9d00d243b98b234145b849.webm?t=1726051539\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2254030/extras/bd54b1c58a9d00d243b98b234145b849.mp4?t=1726051539\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>探索地区<br>游戏有许多难度不同的精彩关卡。探索石器时代的世界、寻找食物，并尽快击败敌人。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2254030/extras/b0a8f7b4400a2d685516d940ae21e45e.poster.avif?t=1726051539\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2254030/extras/b0a8f7b4400a2d685516d940ae21e45e.webm?t=1726051539\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2254030/extras/b0a8f7b4400a2d685516d940ae21e45e.mp4?t=1726051539\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>获得奖励<br>迅速完成关卡可获得道具。当你完成任务时，可以获得宝箱、钻石、各种助推器和许多其他奖励！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2254030/extras/1a79e6a2274d17502b8a93271c449190.poster.avif?t=1726051539\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2254030/extras/1a79e6a2274d17502b8a93271c449190.webm?t=1726051539\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2254030/extras/1a79e6a2274d17502b8a93271c449190.mp4?t=1726051539\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>照顾恐龙<br>喂养可爱的恐龙，以便获得帮助并在石器时代生存。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2254030/extras/d656661bbbc0944c8e8f2b1966aeec6f.poster.avif?t=1726051539\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2254030/extras/d656661bbbc0944c8e8f2b1966aeec6f.webm?t=1726051539\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2254030/extras/d656661bbbc0944c8e8f2b1966aeec6f.mp4?t=1726051539\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
